QuestData.Title: Strike Back
QuestData.Description: As you may have seen, the ritualists in this forest kidnap our people and perform heinous rituals on them. The souls of our fallen now roam as twisted creatures. This sin cannot go unpunished. Kill as many ritualists as you are able, but be sure to strike at the dark demon that leads them.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill $1oa Eredar ritualists and Lady Shahrazad in the Petrified Forest.
